      <title>Plotting Points in the Plane</title>
      <objectives>
	<ul>
	  <li>
	    Plot points in the plane using Cartesian coordinates,
	  </li>
	  <li>
	    Identify the quadrant in which a point lies.
	  </li>
	</ul>
